{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d5cac7e085","title":"转发上海市委关于严防在控诉会上扩大打击面的通报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9b4d497401","index":0,"year":1951,"month":5,"day":23,"articleId":"d5cac7e085"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"76ee14ca63","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d5cac7e085","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共上海市委1951年5月19日关于严防在控诉会上扩大打击面的通报中规定的几条意见是：（一）控诉会的控诉对象一律确定为被捕罪犯（并以罪大恶极的为主）。（二）控诉会不能变成斗争会，不能把打击面扩大到落后分子以及有关生活作风、思想观点方面。（三）控诉会不能在一个基层单位连续不断地召开。一般好好准备召开一次即可。如无具体控诉对象可不召开，以座谈讨论已破获的反革命案件等方法，提高群众的政治认识。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7e68352d0b","type":"title","text":"转发上海市委关于严防在控诉会上扩大打击面的通报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d5cac7e085"},{"id":"76ee14ca63","type":"paragraph","text":"中南、华南、西南、西北、华北、东北各中央局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d5cac7e085"},{"id":"706e81b59e","type":"paragraph","text":"上海市委关于严防在控诉会上扩大打击面的意见”是正确的请你们加以注意。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d5cac7e085"},{"id":"c6ffafbe30","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d5cac7e085"},{"id":"0682d890da","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d5cac7e085"}],"page":{"id":"6e3dd55016","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d5cac7e085","start":325,"end":325}}}},"__N_SSG":true}